  - New installs should create `rental_vendors(rental_vendor_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY, ...)`
  - Existing installs should migrate in `init_schema` by detecting the old `vendor_id` column and renaming it to `rental_vendor_id`
- In [web/app.py](/home/aatish/app/genset/web/app.py) and the rental-only repository/model/service path:
