## API / Data Contract Changes
- Rental-only API contract becomes explicit:
  - `POST /api/rental-vendors` accepts optional `rental_vendor_id` and returns `rental_vendor_id`
  - `PATCH /api/rental-vendors/{rental_vendor_id}` uses the renamed parameter
  - `DELETE /api/rental-vendors/{rental_vendor_id}` uses the renamed parameter
  - `GET /api/rental-vendors` returns rental records keyed with `rental_vendor_id`
- Retail vendor APIs stay as-is to avoid breaking booking-related flows.

